    "English": "Exclusive Spacecraft",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属飞船",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊太空船"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A unique and exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">starship</span>, commemorating completion of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Omega</span> expedition.<br><br>This unusual starship is optimized for effortless gliding during flight, while a localized vector field allows the craft to hover above solid planes.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘独一无二的专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，纪念你完成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">欧米茄</span>远征。<br><br>这艘不同寻常的飞船经过了优化改造，因此能够在飞行期间毫无阻力地顺畅滑行，除此以外一个局部范围的矢量场将允许飞船飘浮在实体平面之上。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">领取</span>这艘飞船并将其添加至你的收藏，或者与你的当前飞船进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，通过快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘獨一無二的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，用以紀念 <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Omega</span> 探險的完成。<br><br>這艘不凡的太空船經過巧手改造後，飛行時不但平穩順暢，而且局部向量場使其可以懸浮在堅實的平面上方。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
